name: Windsurf Editor
snippet:
Tomorrow's editor, today. Windsurf Editor is the first AI agent-powered IDE that keeps developers in the flow. Available today on Mac, Windows, and Linux.
We adopted the Windsurf Editor as part of our strategy to support developer productivity and streamline how we build at scale. We are excited to see how this collaboration can help us move faster while maintaining the technical excellence our users expect.
